<p>The onboarding process begins with a strategic assessment to understand your current content landscape, sales cycle, and technical infrastructure. We then execute rapid foundational setup focusing on high-impact authority pages, structured schema, and conversational architecture. This process typically takes a few days to a week, after which continuous optimization aligns ongoing efforts with revenue goals.</p>
</div>
